snippet.textDisplay:
Hello good night excuse my message so meaningless but I have time being a person full of admiration for you, I do not want to sound flattering or anything like that but I would like to tell you my story and well hopefully one day you can read the message and take me into account. .
My name is Jazmin Villegas Morales I am of Mexican nationality I live in a state called Guanajuato I am currently married and I am 21 years old,
From my young age I remember going through difficult things in my family, my mother from lower class and my middle class father, when I was born when my mother was 25 my parents had nothing, my paternal grandparents gave them a roof for a time but on many occasions my mother was treated badly by my grandparents so we had to go to live in a small wooden house their measurements were 3 by 5 meters we lived many difficult times, my dad had to leave us Some years because he went to work in the United States illegally, it was the only way out of poverty and after many years my father returned when I was 15, many years of my children lived without a father figure I was only with my mom but when my dad came back by then I left high school and since he couldn't afford to pay for my studies he took me out of study and put me to work, since then I worked in a cocktail restaurant, in a carpentry shop, in a flower shop, in a butcher shop, I had a small pantry shop, worked in auto parts factory, in vegetable factories, held many positions and learned to work in anything assigned to me, but in my house always lived with many problems many times I thought that my dad did not want me that I was not good enough to be his daughter, many times he yelled at me, insulted me and made me feel useless, he was very strict with me and Many times he made me cry, but I never let him down, I never did anything he did not always try to make him proud of me but it was never enough.
All the time I spent working and when I went somewhere he got angry and told me that I should do things at home but never had time for me, I felt that I never enjoyed anything I lived surrounded by much sadness and despair, my only wishes they were that one day I was free or that I could enjoy, by then I already knew my current husband and one day decided to leave my house, I did not know where to go, I did not want to cause more problems or be a burden to Someone but my husband held out his hand and told me to live with him and his family.
Soon we got married by marital status and we have almost 2 years of marriage but to date we still live in my in-laws' house we have not had the opportunity to build or buy a house, wages in Mexico are very low unfortunately and the houses I am Very expensive and very small at the moment my husband's salary is $ 1, 700 per week the equivalent of 90 dollars, it is very little and that is the reason why we do not have a home of our own, today we are going through difficult times since that we have nowhere to go since several echos have passed with their parents, therefore we have to leave.
I would like to be able to get ahead and fulfill my dreams of forming a family and having a home without having to disturb anyone, and my message comes from the bottom of my heart I have been following him for several years and I see that he is a noble person, I ask from my heart to help me please, to help me with a job so that I can build my home here in Mexico, a job where I can earn well to be able to fulfill the dream of having my home, I have been unable to sleep for nights to think about what I should do to get ahead, getting a job in the United States by contract is very difficult and most of the time they only hire men, and that way I will never be able to raise all the money that the house costs that I would like to have since it costs around 300,000 dollars ...
Please help me by giving me the opportunity for a better paid job I ask with all my heart and with all my strength ...
Thank you
Jazmin Villegas Morales

snippet.textDisplay: Jeffree is finally going to release a nude eyeshadow palette soon. Last week on Instagram when announcing BloodLust, he teased that he is finally coming out with a certain eyeshadow palette that people have been requesting from him for years.
